---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout seo={{ title: "Privacy Policy", description: "HealthPulse privacy policy — how we handle your data" }}>
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

		<div class="prose prose-lg prose-healthcare max-w-none">
			<p>
				HealthPulse ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information in compliance with the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023 (DPDP Act) and applicable Indian laws.
			</p>

			<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
			<h3>Information you provide</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Newsletter subscription:</strong> Email address and optionally your name</li>
				<li><strong>Demo requests:</strong> Name, email, phone, hospital name, and role (for MedBrains HMS inquiries)</li>
				<li><strong>Comments/feedback:</strong> Any information you voluntarily submit</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Page views, referral source, country, device type, and browser (via privacy-respecting analytics — no cookies, no personal tracking)</li>
				<li><strong>Technical:</strong> IP address (anonymized), browser type, operating system</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>To send you the newsletter you subscribed to</li>
				<li>To respond to demo requests or inquiries</li>
				<li>To understand aggregate readership patterns (not individual tracking)</li>
				<li>To improve our content and user experience</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
			<p>
				We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. We may share data with:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Ghost CMS:</strong> For newsletter delivery (self-hosted, data stays on our servers)</li>
				<li><strong>Analytics provider:</strong> Aggregate, anonymized usage data only</li>
				<li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> If required by law or legal process</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>4. Your Rights (DPDP Act)</h2>
			<p>Under the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023, you have the right to:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Access your personal data we hold</li>
				<li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
				<li>Request erasure of your data</li>
				<li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
				<li>Lodge a grievance with the Data Protection Board of India</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
			<p>
				Newsletter subscriptions are retained until you unsubscribe. Demo request data is retained for 12 months. Analytics data is aggregated and anonymized.
			</p>

			<h2>6. Cookies</h2>
			<p>
				We use minimal cookies — only those essential for website functionality. We do not use tracking cookies or third-party advertising cookies.
			</p>

			<h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
			<p>
				HealthPulse is not directed at children under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors.
			</p>

			<h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
			<p>
				We may update this policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
			</p>

			<h2>9. Contact</h2>
			<p>
				For privacy-related inquiries or to exercise your rights:
				<a href="mailto:privacy@healthpulse.medbrains.in">privacy@healthpulse.medbrains.in</a>
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
